InsertDecFloatTypes: INSERT INTO DECFLOAT_TEST (F_ID, F_DECFLOAT16, F_DECFLOAT16_NULLABLE, F_DECFLOAT34, F_DECFLOAT34_NULLABLE, F_NAME) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
SelectDecFloatById: SELECT F_DECFLOAT16, F_DECFLOAT16_NULLABLE, F_DECFLOAT34, F_DECFLOAT34_NULLABLE, F_NAME FROM DECFLOAT_TEST WHERE F_ID = ?
SelectAllDecFloat: SELECT F_ID, F_DECFLOAT16, F_DECFLOAT16_NULLABLE, F_DECFLOAT34, F_DECFLOAT34_NULLABLE, F_NAME FROM DECFLOAT_TEST
UpdateDecFloat34: UPDATE DECFLOAT_TEST SET F_DECFLOAT34 = ? WHERE F_ID = ?
SelectDecFloat34Greater: SELECT F_DECFLOAT34, F_NAME FROM DECFLOAT_TEST WHERE F_DECFLOAT34 > ?
